            <li id="m1">Junior Member</li>
            For skaters under 18 years old. Junior Members receive all the benefits of Kingsgate Skating Club, in addition to the privileges authorized in the USFS Constitution, with the exception of voting or holding office. Junior Members may have a parent vote for them.
            <li id="m1">Senior Member</li>
            For skaters 18 to 54 years old. Senior Members receive all the benefits of Kingsgate Skating Club, in addition to the privileges authorized in the USFS Constitution. Senior Members have voting privileges and can hold office.
