            For skaters 55 years and older. Plus 55 Members receive all the benefits of Senior Members, with reduced membership dues.
            <li id="m1">Non-Skating Parent</li>
            For non-skating parents of Junior Members who wish to join Kingsgate Skating Club. The benefits are voting privileges and holding office. LTS parents can also join.
            <li id="m1">Associate Member</li>
            For full USFS members of another club who would like to enjoy some benefits of Kingsgate Skating Club. Associate Members receive discounted punch cards for ice time and pay home club test fees. Associate Members cannot vote.
            <li id="m1">Professional Club Member</li>
            For coaches who derive an income from skating and teach private students. Coaches must go through the USFS coach registration process and receive the &quot;green light&quot; before applying for membership.
